{"tid":970582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港好亂 太子道東平治遭兩寶馬閘停　7刀手落車斬人","createTime":"2019-01-06T03:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T09:01:25.000Z","uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff950087df8729e3d4b43e18b10ec5cc80035c50","tid":970582,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:05:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子道東平治遭兩寶馬閘停　7刀手落車斬人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日(5日)下午3時許，4名男子駕乘一輛白色平治房車，沿太子道東往觀塘方向行駛，至彩虹邨金碧樓對開，突被一輛銀色寶馬房車衝前把平治閘停，未幾尾隨另一輛銀色寶馬馳至，高速猛撞平治，平治180度打「白鴿轉」後橫亘快線。<br />\n<br />\n此時2輛寶馬跳下7名戴上鴨舌帽、口罩、手套，分別手持利刀及鐵通的彪形大漢，包圍平治向車身及擋風玻璃猛扑，惟平治司機及乘客鎖上車門，刀手無計可施，其後跳上其中一輛寶馬逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n警方趕至封鎖現場，並在附近一帶展開圍捕，其中平治上2名男子報稱受傷，即場接受救護員敷治後，分別送往伊利沙伯醫院及聯合醫院治理。至下午4時許，警方在九龍灣協調道近啟東道變電站對開，發現懷疑刀手乘坐的寶馬房車，惟暫未發現刀手蹤影。受事件影響，運輸署宣布太子道東往觀塘方向近彩虹邨的部分行車線封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車線行車，現時上址交通擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=7c4bd16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=24557844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=a5701d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=94682a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=154d4f33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_06p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=4d53e61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_07p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=cc76833c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_08p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_08p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=2f6388f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_09p.jpg?20190106051603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105155814521-0105_00822_001_09p.jpg%3F20190106051603&h=ae46edd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/2019